name: Explore The Wonders of Wellington from a unique vantage point
description: I will guide you around Wellington, showing you all the must sees of the city. Offering a unique travel experience you won't forget. Skilled in photography with a creative flare I have an interest in capturing the beauty in our everyday world. I will teach you how to create wonderful images and learn photographic skills that will carry you through your travels and enhance your memories of Wellington.
